<p>
The ideal candidate will have:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Bachelor&#39;s Degree in Computer Science/Information Technology/Engineering or similar.&nbsp; MBA is a plus.</li>
<li>
At least 3 year(s) of working experience in the Video Conferencing, Telepresence or Telecommunication and managed services a Sales Engineer or Product Manager.</li>
<li>
Technical knowledge in one or more of the following of Cisco, Tandberg, Codian, Polycom, Life Size, TCP/IP, Video Standards, Windows, Networking, Hardware design, mission Critical-High Availability Concepts.</li>
<li>
Excellent interpersonal, presentation and conversational skills</li>
<li>
Strong written and oral skills</li>
<li>
Ability to lead technical presentations</li>
</ul>
